Object.Name: Notecard
Object.Nickname: This is the [b]BETA[/b] mod. Do not use for tournaments.
Object.Description:
Historically, we've updated the beta mod less periodically, and it's been used for online tournaments. 

- The beta mod will be [b]UNSTABLE[/b] for tournament play; we intend to make lots of changes, and that will cause lots of bugs.

- Tournaments should [b]ONLY[/b] use the stable mod: https://go.swlegion.dev/stable/
